    "Some research questions follow from our discussion:",
    "How does the integration of GenAI affect organizational culture, especially concerning knowledge sharing and collaboration among employees? 2.",
    "How does the pervasive use of GenAI affect the development and maintenance of social networks for knowledge creation within organizations? 3.",
    "How do employees judge the validity and relevance of knowledge? 4.",
